.*****************************************************************************
.*    Program      : F05PTDET                                                *
.*    Description  : Conversion patdetaf to new File layout                  *
.*                                                                           *
.*    Author       : J.Tan                                                   *
.*    Date         : 26/08/2014                                              *
.*    Modifications:                                                         *
.*                                                                           *
.*****************************************************************************
.
          INC       STD001FD
.
FINDFILE  FILE      ASCII, FIXED=256
.
.
. Old File definition
