PTDERPAY  FORM      12.2   8        82    Amount to be repaid
PTDEFREQ  DIM       3      3        90    Frequency of Payment (Cat FP)
.                                         eg.Daily,Weekly,Fortnightly,Monthly,Q
.                                         uaterly
